videos.description: North Carolina guard Joel Berry III comes up with the steal and drives to the basket for the contested layup.
videos.headline: Berry goes coast to coast for the tough finish

videos.description: Kenny Williams gets the pass in the paint and hits the layup going through contact.
videos.headline: UNC's Williams takes the contact, connects on the and-1 layup

videos.description: UNC forward Garrison Brooks gets the pass in the paint and throws down a one-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Brooks gets pass and delivers one-handed slam

videos.description: Kenny Williams collects the offensive rebound and puts in the layup with the first half winding down.
videos.headline: Williams' putback just before half gives Heels 13 point edge

videos.description: North Carolina guard Joel Berry III tosses pass from half court to Kenny Williams for the layup
videos.headline: Berry throws alley-oop to Williams for layup
